cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.SE, cs.CR

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper discusses the use of Mobile ad-hoc network (MANET) in the Internet of Things (IoT) and its connection to cloud computing. 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is also likely as the paper discusses the decentralized system of MANET and its connection to cloud computing. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper discusses the data handling and resource management in the IoT-Cloud-MANET framework. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper discusses the integration of mobile apps for connecting smart devices of MANET to cloud. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a possible category as the paper mentions providing secure communication on the internet of smart devices using MANET concept in 5G.
